<p>Never publish without human review. Google rewards helpful, experience-driven content. Raw AI output ranks poorly and damages trust. Learn how to <a href="/blog/humanize-ai-content/">humanize AI content</a> the right way.</p>
<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> AI alone produces generic content. Humans alone produce limited volume. The combination produces volume and quality. Skip the human edit and your content joins the flood of low-quality pages that Google filters out.</p>
